{"tid":308876,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急外地酒店及信用卡問題求助","createTime":"2017-07-04T14:10:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-04T20:21:08.000Z","uid":8497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5868c2d9ec8d2a987266ab208dd9f421a077b1bb","tid":308876,"uid":8497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T14:10:18.000Z","msg":"我原本係Accorhotels既官網book左係巴黎住ibis<br />\n由於上網需要用信用卡book既關係<br />\n而且每次簽賬都要香港電話sms確認<br />\n所以頭兩次payment都因為收唔到sms而失敗<br />\n所以第三次我問係香港屋企人既信用卡而比錢<br />\n最後book完屋企人收到銀行確認既訊息<br />\n而亦都有顯示左酒店預約成功<br />\n<br />\n但可惜既係我打預約酒店時email打錯左所以收唔到confirmation email<br />\n為左穩陣我地到左巴黎亦即刻衝去酒店<br />\n點知佢地話個預約失敗左<br />\n話因為payment出錯<br />\n佢亦都話佢地無收到筆錢<br />\n因此我地重新係酒店入面再比番一樣既價錢去訂酒店<br />\n<br />\n問題就係呢到<br />\n屋企人已經多次聯絡銀行<br />\n銀行亦已確認的確過左筆數比法國呢面<br />\n但酒店呢面話搵唔到有呢方面既資料<br />\n事件已經搞左好多日<br />\nD法國佬效率又慢<br />\n我而家應該可以點做盡快令酒店可以盡快退錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9633afe6a195508561a154ff8a2a400fcf13f983","tid":308876,"uid":8497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T14:19:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4645d3e7361e4ef8d6059e426cfdad7612f1064","tid":308876,"uid":8497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T14:32:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b172e3c67e15068880c5879730a92dfc20e7d6e8","tid":308876,"uid":8497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T20:05:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed62137d2a686c64d8edcd1e257351e6333abbaf","tid":308876,"uid":115059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T20:21:08.000Z","msg":"真係唯有打hotline 不停打 去搵人幫你再check"}]}